text: Gheorghe Enache (22 September 1934 - 1971) was a Romanian sports shooter. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:1971 deaths Category:Romanian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Romania Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bucharest
